# Task 2 – Pre-requisites

## Project
Credit Card Approval Prediction Using Machine Learning

## Objective

Set up the required software tools and Python libraries for developing the Credit Card Approval Prediction system.

## Software Used

- Anaconda Navigator
- PyCharm

## Python Libraries

- NumPy
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Flask
- XGBoost

## Installation

```bash
pip install numpy pandas matplotlib seaborn scikit-learn flask xgboost
```

## Development Environment

- Python 3.x
- Anaconda Navigator
- PyCharm IDE

## Outcome

The development environment is configured successfully, enabling data preprocessing, machine learning model development, visualization, and Flask-based deployment.

## Conclusion

All required tools and libraries have been installed and configured successfully, providing a complete environment for building the Credit Card Approval Prediction project.
